     activity)<BR>
E. Interpersonal Assessment (class discussion on<BR>
     sun energy)<BR>
F. Intrapersonal Assessment (<CITE>water cycle </CITE>
activity)<BR>
G. Reflective Assessment (personal journal entry)  <BR>
