<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=5><CENTER><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Lesson Plan  #5 - Invasive Species</FONT></CENTER></FONT></B> <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <CENTER><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#290A64"><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="lespsix">Task Analysis</A></A></FONT></CENTER><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <CENTER><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#290A64"><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="assmnt">Summative Assessment</A></FONT></CENTER><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="assmnt#port6">Portfolio Assessment</A></CENTER>
<DD>     <DD>     <!-- Horizontal Line Tag --><HR WIDTH=100% SIZE=3 NOSHADE>
<DD>     <DD>     
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Lesson Target:</FONT></FONT></B>   <BR>
<DD>     <DD>       Species Invasion  <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Science Concept:</FONT></FONT></B><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Invasion  Migration <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Food Chains  Competition<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Science Skills:</FONT></FONT></B><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Observation and Gathering <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Charting and Illustrating<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Analyze and Predict<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Interdisciplinary Connection:</FONT></FONT></B><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Geography, History <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     Duration: 1 week<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Lesson outcomes:</FONT></FONT></B><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <STRONG> </STRONG>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4>Students will:</FONT></B><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <OL>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Define exotic species and native species<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Gather and Identify exotic species<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Chart and illustrate exotic species migration    <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Discuss the impacts on native species<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Discuss the economic costs of invasive species<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Discuss solutions to control or terminate exotics  <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     </OL>
<DD>     <DD>     <B><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FFCC33">Overview:</FONT></FONT></B><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     In this lesson students will increase their awareness of human introduced exotic species in the  Oswegotchie River ecosystem . Students will discuss the consequences of the exotics and what future actions might be taken in regard to introduced species.<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <STRONG>Activity: <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     </STRONG>
<DD>     <DD>     <STRONG></STRONG>
<DD>     <DD>     "Aquatic Roots"  from  <EM>Project Aquatic</EM>
<DD>     <DD>       p 100<STRONG> </STRONG>
