<DOCHDR>
http://www.potsdam.edu:80/EDUC/GLC/river/bio/blesson/lesfor 137.143.111.2 19970209015338 text/html 3936
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.144804@www.potsdam.edu>
