<center>
<strong>XIII.  AFFIRMATIVE ACTION</strong></center>
<dd><dl><!-- 0 --><BR>

<dt>A.  <A HREF="S13A-D.html#13A"><b>EQUAL OPPORTUNITY POLICY OF THE STATE UNIVERSITY OF NEW YORK (SUNY)</b></a>
<dt><br>
<dt>B.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13B"><b>EQUAL OPPORTUNITY AND AFFIRMATIVE ACTION POLICY OF THE STATE UNIVERSITY OF NEW YORK, AT POTSDAM</b></a>
<dt><br>
<dt>C.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13C"><b>COMMITMENT TO QUALITY</b></a>

<dt><br>
<dt>D.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D"><b>RECRUITMENT PROCEDURES</b>
