<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR="#4E238A">Lesson outcomes:</FONT><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     
<DD>     <DD>     <H3> </H3>
<DD>     <DD>     <!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR="#4E238A">Students will:</FONT><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <OL>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Recognize the impact humans have on their environment <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Recognize the impact the environment has on humans <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Investigate the quality of the food we eat<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI> Discuss health problems associated with pollution    <DD>    <DD>     <LI> Discuss solutions to pollution problems<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Actively clean their environment<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <LI>  Realize they can improve environmental conditions<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     </OL>
<DD>     <DD>     <!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR="#4E238A">Overview:</FONT><BR>
<DD>     <DD>     In this lesson students will observe irresponsible human actions and study their consequences. 
Students will also discuss possible sollutions.<BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <BR>
<DD>     <DD>     <STRONG>Activity:</STRONG>
