<BR>
<BR>
<center>
<strong>XIII.  AFFIRMATIVE ACTION</strong></center>
<dd><dl><!-- 0 --><BR>

<dt>A.  <A HREF="S13A-D.html#13A"><b>EQUAL OPPORTUNITY POLICY OF THE STATE UNIVERSITY OF NEW YORK (SUNY)</b></a>
<dt><br>
<dt>B.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13B"><b>EQUAL OPPORTUNITY AND AFFIRMATIVE ACTION POLICY OF THE STATE UNIVERSITY OF NEW YORK, AT POTSDAM</b></a>
<dt><br>
<dt>C.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13C"><b>COMMITMENT TO QUALITY</b></a>

<dt><br>
<dt>D.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D"><b>RECRUITMENT PROCEDURES</b>
</a><dt><br>
<dd><dl><!-- 1 -->
	<dt>1.	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1"><i>INITIATING THE SEARCH</i></a>
<dt><br>
<dd><dl><!-- 2 -->
		<dt>a)	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1a">Recruitment Request</a>
<dt><br>
		<dt>b)	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1b">Advertising</a>
			<dt><br>
<dd><dl><!-- 3 -->
			<dt>i)	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1bi">Faculty Searches</a>
<dt><br>
			<dt>ii)	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1bii">Professional and Management Searches</a>
</dl><!-- 3 -->
<dt><br>
		<dt>c)	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1c">Composition of the Search Committee</a>
<dt><br>
		<dt>d)	<A HREF="S13A-D.html#13D1d">Search Committee Charge</a>
