<TITLE>
Macintosh training sessions - Spring '96</TITLE>
<!-- Created by J. Upham.  1/12/96-->
</HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"> 
<CENTER><IMG  SRC="/DCTM/DCTMlogo.gif"></CENTER><p>
<CENTER><H1>Macintosh Training Sessions</H1></CENTER>
<center><B><FONT SIZE=5>Spring 96 schedule</FONT></B></CENTER><br>

<HR SIZE=4>
<p>


The Macintosh training sessions will be held as follows:<P>
<DL>
<DD>      <B>Monday</B> - Kellas Computer Classroom (<A HREF="http://www.potsdam.edu/dctm/cybertour-it/kellas/kellas100b.html">Kellas 100B</A>)<BR>
5:00 - 7:00 p. m.: Basic operations of using Macintosh computers<BR>
7:00 - 9:00 p. m.: Email and Internet via the Mac computers<BR><BR>

<DD>      <B>Tuesday</B> - Carson Computer Classroom (<A HREF="http://www.potsdam.edu/dctm/cybertour-it/carson/carson101.html">Carson 101</A>)<BR>
5:00 - 7:00 p. m.: Making a basic Web page<BR><BR>

<DD>      <B>Thursday</B> - Kellas Computer Classroom (<A HREF="http://www.potsdam.edu/dctm/cybertour-it/kellas/kellas100b.html">Kellas 100B</A>)<BR>
7:00 - 9:00 p. m.: Basic operations of using Microsoft Word (word-processing)<BR>
</DL>
<P>
<HR WIDTH=30%>

<P>
Registration for all sessions <B>is required</B>.  You may register in any of the following ways:

<UL>
<LI>drop by the <A HREF="http://www.potsdam.edu/dctm/cybertour-it/crumb/levitt.html">Levitt Center</A>
<LI>call <B>267-2215</B> (Levitt Center Helpdesk) or <B>267-2083</B> (Carson HelpDesk)
<LI>use our <A HREF="/dctm/presentations/fall95workshops/MacWkshop-request-form.html">electronic registration form</A>.<P>
Please note that you must register 24 hours in advance for all Web Page sessions.
</UL>
<HR SIZE=4>
